{"tid":1610631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"手足覺悟 偽勇武 問題","createTime":"2019-10-01T18:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T07:36:44.000Z","uid":11028,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1b8cccc36c007a3ce27b78d22a27069f33bb8631","tid":1610631,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:34:59.000Z","msg":"其實之前都見過好多人開post講呢類人<br />\n但我今日終於親身遇到 真係有啲嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道自己大概咩料 所以今日做救火<br />\n但今日喺狗推嘅時候 大家當然爭相走避<br />\n但我真係無諗過有偽勇武出現 跑到快過保特<br />\n完全撞飛咗我 我差啲跌低俾人踩<br />\n亦因為咁有啲皮外傷 之後變埋最前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實手足未有心理準備 唔需要企咁前 冇人會怪你<br />\n但你偽勇武係真係會影響到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後面啲人見你跑 會更驚慌<br />\n亦都會令人有錯覺 有勇武cover 俾和理非慢慢退<br />\n點撚知 原來冇勇武 咁其他手足就隨時俾狗咬<br />\n要做好覺悟先上前 唔係要你預咗俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔係狗有少少舉動 就閃電俠咁<br />\n<br />\n另外就係塞撚住哂 搞到走得好慢<br />\n希望和理非唔好企得太埋 要企疏啲 一個手位<br />\n咁樣大家及前線手足先有路可退<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我被撞飛同慢慢塞之下<br />\n聽到發射催淚彈嘅聲係非常之近<br />\n我個下真係心都離一離 知道狗一追 我就係咁先<br />\n<br />\n我好多謝大家肯企出黎 但有部分手足仲係嘉年華心態<br />\n打下卡 無危機感 食下花生咁 衣著都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家仲記得點解要出黎<br />\n我哋唔可以令過咗身受咗傷斷送前途嘅手足白白犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預咗俾人屌分化撚 但呢啲問題係真係需要正視<br />\n做法不完美 可接受 要改善<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">提出問題唔係當分化啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong>"},{"pid":"de39f40f11057479a8adbb3c7ad03dc20ce78ae6","tid":1610631,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:03:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bdc10e15bd4f92182eb4e2686c70384866f958d","tid":1610631,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:04:16.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5550feb492f6b804d1964be8cf439e6f5a081ecc","tid":1610631,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:06:06.000Z","msg":"好心啦， 做隊友就唔好成日埋怨人啦。 最多叫唔敢打既人企遠小小"},{"pid":"0f3c69fc3ab0c7a273301170caf55a8a7f707352","tid":1610631,"uid":11028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5550feb492f6b804d1964be8cf439e6f5a081ecc","tid":1610631,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:06:06.000Z","msg":"好心啦， 做隊友就唔好成日埋怨人啦。 最多叫唔敢打既人企遠小小"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:26:01.000Z","msg":"唔係話埋怨<br />\n塞住嘅問題係一直都有<br />\n<br />\n偽勇武呢排係多咗好多<br />\n唔到退嗰刻都唔知原來係偽勇武<br />\n我真係好無諗過可以咁自私撞開人推開人走先<br />\n知道自己能力不足都唔應該企咁前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我開呢個post 係因為呢排成日出現呢啲嘢<br />\n想大家自己諗下適合咩崗位大概點做咁"},{"pid":"aa538f833bf6af6fa732cad6759f4a3a7de6866f","tid":1610631,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T22:58:09.000Z","msg":"晨早一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a578a1c6ae80b9b6fa4747ec7299a776f72f9a","tid":1610631,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:01:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"489a8b59edc356f82534a513e779b424bee3d5c1","tid":1610631,"uid":254388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:02:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12b7275ef474208ed778393e067ceebcbb43f7d9","tid":1610631,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:03:42.000Z","msg":"是"},{"pid":"d4d0609eea820f2a4ac8d7df9e1b9112e6668a8a","tid":1610631,"uid":263542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:13:01.000Z","msg":"琴日沙田新城市巴士站果度又係咁，我搬磚都搬到手軟，地下咁多磚，前邊話走就走，丟都唔丟一個，咁我地搬黎做乜？"},{"pid":"d85662f486036153e5b5d179eb5532572f4bdaa7","tid":1610631,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"489a8b59edc356f82534a513e779b424bee3d5c1","tid":1610631,"uid":254388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:02:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:55:03.000Z","msg":"Agger<br />\n走就走得快 做勇武嘢嘅真係好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f40b9fef34e497348fd0fc686df5628ef52620","tid":1610631,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:20:26.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推 好多人仲去返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb1259c664070e4fc408a72f2ca7b80fc4da358","tid":1610631,"uid":41974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:23:30.000Z","msg":"組隊打狗 人人有責<br />\n<br />\n見狗即可舉手召喚手足"},{"pid":"5bc1e34aaee1de4635e86abc422fb20afdb8ae62","tid":1610631,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:06:11.000Z","msg":"其實有裝 狗放煙真係唔驚<br />\n退係因為知道狗喺好撚近嘅位置<br />\n但偽勇武要認真諗下自己適合咩位置"},{"pid":"c97e88719172374c388bcc3b42912ee9cb0122c6","tid":1610631,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4d0609eea820f2a4ac8d7df9e1b9112e6668a8a","tid":1610631,"uid":263542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:13:01.000Z","msg":"琴日沙田新城市巴士站果度又係咁，我搬磚都搬到手軟，地下咁多磚，前邊話走就走，丟都唔丟一個，咁我地搬黎做乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:16:57.000Z","msg":"其實爬咗幾個鐘連登<br />\n發覺沉日幾個區都有類似嘅問題<br />\n多謝巴打你嘅付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我哋唔可以氣餒<br />\n我都好想多啲手足有覺悟幫下手<br />\n但真係急唔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終香港人都係喺呢百幾日逼住成長<br />\n對神獸出現 更多魔法 不合作運動嘅支持大大上升<br />\n我諗嚟緊係要等佢哋自己覺悟<br />\n跳出自己嘅comfort zone 出擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢樣嘢係好難亦都要好長嘅時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b8cdb9670b4041d38c0af494ccd8cbf2932bb4","tid":1610631,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:17:13.000Z","msg":"對準政權 全民公投實行雙普選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609445</a>"},{"pid":"bbd042e7a95410780fe61ebd16bad4ee5cf785ac","tid":1610631,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:40:46.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f136557b2bff818d292917bf7c5d44b26560a06","tid":1610631,"uid":51682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:51:05.000Z","msg":"唉....<br />\n<br />\n我朋友冇帶咀都仲前過成班帶撚哂咀嘅<br />\n<br />\n一跑少少,成班就鳩跑到閪咁撚快,跑成百米都唔回頭望下,根本冇狗<br />\n<br />\n灰灰地開始"},{"pid":"56f955e3256351f10fe062581588293a5e45812c","tid":1610631,"uid":214298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:43:12.000Z","msg":"多謝手足付出 辛苦你啦<br />\n尋日有狗一過黎<br />\n所有人即刻跑走<br />\n我上左裝準備去前面擋一擋<br />\n點知俾班和理非／偽勇武係後面推（我唔知係邊個）<br />\n成個人跌落地（仲要落緊樓梯）<br />\n個眼罩俾人踩爛左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過衣裝問題真係講左好耐<br />\n和理非又好勇武又好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該好好保護自己</span></span><br />\n著條熱褲背心淨sport bar出黎想點<br />\n已經唔係有無裝備既問題<br />\n<br />\n依家係出黎戰鬥唔係玩<br />\n無人想俾狗乘機抽水<br />\n非分化<br />\n但勞煩各位著好啲保護自己安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99af234e7dfc6c87a5d178f71a33db68385c9a9","tid":1610631,"uid":11028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:36:44.000Z","msg":"好 係要鼓勵佢哋<br />\n新手勇武唔好再9跑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}